01:24:20,281 --> 01:24:22,943
Thank God I made it in time.

557
01:24:26,855 --> 01:24:27,685
Who's he?

558
01:24:30,058 --> 01:24:31,047
Mononobe.

559
01:24:32,360 --> 01:24:35,796
He stayed up all night,
encouraging me on the phone.

560
01:24:40,502 --> 01:24:41,867
I get it.

561
01:24:42,771 --> 01:24:43,931
What?

562
01:24:44,572 --> 01:24:47,234
Mononobe!
Do you have a girlfriend?

563
01:24:47,375 --> 01:24:48,774
Aiko!

564
01:24:49,344 --> 01:24:54,008
Who, me? I'm totally available.

565
01:25:19,741 --> 01:25:21,106
It's dawn.

566
01:25:26,581 --> 01:25:28,276
It was a long night.

567
01:25:30,318 --> 01:25:31,910
It really was.

568
01:30:05,226 --> 01:30:06,523
''Ashikari Hot Spring
is just a fiction.''

569
01:30:06,661 --> 01:30:07,855
''It is not related to
any real village and place.''

